    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> in a large bowl, then stir in your <strong>harissa paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – this is your<strong> harissa stock</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>couscous </strong>to the harissa stock, cover and set aside</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
