      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a small pan over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your<strong> pumpkin seeds</strong> and toast for 3 min</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p><p>Once done, set the <strong>toasted pumpkin seeds</strong> aside until serving</p>",
      "order": 5,
