      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>beetroot juice</strong>, <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander</strong> and 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp] </span>[4 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Fluff the <strong>cooked couscous</strong> with a fork – this is your <strong>harissa couscous</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
